South Korea’s Ministry of Food and Drug Safety (MFDS) issued a warning urging people to stop eating deep fried toothpicks. Videos of people preparing and eating the toothpicks have gone viral on TikTok and Instagram in recent months, and appear to be especially popular in South Korea.&nbsp;
“This is not a product to eat!” South Korea’s Ministry of Food and Drug Safety wrote in a post on X.

